## 🛠 Module Description

### Inputs

| Signal | Width | Description |
|---------|------|-------------|
| clk | 1 | System clock |
| reset | 1 | Active-high asynchronous reset |
| up_down | 1 | Counter direction control |

### Output

| Signal | Width | Description |
|---------|------|-------------|
| q | 4 | 4-bit counter output |

---

## ⚙ Operation

### Reset

When `reset = 1`

```
q = 0000
```

---

### Count Up

When

```
up_down = 1
```

Counter sequence:

```
0000
0001
0010
0011
0100
...
1111
0000
```

---

### Count Down

When

```
up_down = 0
```

Counter sequence:

```
1111
1110
1101
1100
1011
...
0001
0000
1111
```

---

## 🏗 Hardware Architecture

```
                 +----------------------+
                 |     4-bit Register   |
                 +----------+-----------+
                            |
                            |
                            v
                   +------------------+
                   | +1       -1      |
                   |                  |
                   +--------+---------+
                            ^
                            |
                      up_down Control
```

The control signal selects whether the counter increments or decrements on every positive clock edge.

